    <h3>Time Selection</h3>
    <p>We activated now a Swarm L1b product and a time interval on the 30. September 2014 for you </p>
    <p>Did you notice the <strong>time slider</strong> at the bottom of the page? You can see the availability of the selected product there.</p>
    <p>Try stretching the time interval at its ends or draw a new one and watch how the Swarm data visualisation is updated on the globe.</p>
    <p>You can zoom in/out in time by using the mouse wheel over the time slider as well as pan by clicking and dragging where the dates are displayed.</p>
    <p>A more in depth analysis of the data can be done with the analytics viewer, keep on scrolling to see it in action.</p>
</section>
