    <h3>Analytics Viewer</h3>
    <p>We now opened the split view. It can be switched in the <strong>Tools</strong> Widget by clicking on the Split Screen button.</p>
    <p>As you can see the selected Swarm data (product and time) is displayed as scatter plot.</p>
    <p>You can select multiple parameters for visualisation on the y Axis as well as against which parameter you want them to be plotted on the x Axis.</p>
    <p>Play around with the Analytics Viewer to get accostumed to the available functionality.</p>
    <p>This is just the initial tutorial for the VirES Prototype, additional explanation of available features will be added soon!</p>
</section>


